name: Midnight 01 (Deep Sea Diver)
description: This artwork is based on King Krule's lyrics in his song called "Midnight 01 (Deep Sea Diver)", the lyrics is touched my feelings so tough that day when I draw it, the day I feeling so much pressure about anything that going on my life. My love-life, anxiety, feeling depressed everyday, feeling disrespect by other, poor, working with worthless salary, un-productive on producing some work of art, and I just listening to music, eat, and sleep. But, when the lyrics passed me, suddenly I felt some feelings, it feels like I've been tought that I have to swim more deep to my work of art.
